511
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:11,180
I see.

512
00:37:14,179 --> 00:37:21,159
In your heart, this is the only accusation
you can pin on me, right?

513
00:37:21,159 --> 00:37:26,059
But when you were little,
you were so well-behaved and listened to me.

514
00:37:26,059 --> 00:37:32,539
