control me so strictly?

520
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:56,800
When I was little and you got drunk,
you looked at me and said,

521
00:37:56,800 --> 00:38:01,479
"Jiang Meng Chu, it's my fault.

522
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:07,800
