531
00:38:35,019 --> 00:38:36,739
You can't mention him like this!

532
00:38:36,739 --> 00:38:41,079
Jiang Qiao Xi, do you think this honors
your brother? Your dead brother?

533
00:38:41,079 --> 00:38:44,599
