534
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:46,039
What are you saying?

535
00:38:46,039 --> 00:38:49,420
Meng Chu had your eyes and shared your blood.

536
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:50,656
He wouldn't think this way.

537
00:38:50,656 --> 00:38:55,260
Yes, Jiang Meng Chu shared my blood and my eyes.

538
00:38:55,260 --> 00:38:56,639
My skin, my bones, my flesh.

539
00:38:56,639 --> 00:38:58,500
